<title>User Interface</title>
<p>This page explains all options for configuring the User Interface in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Theme</title>
        <p>The theme for the user interface.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: System</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Prevent Suspend</title>
        <p>Parabolic will prevent the computer from sleeping while downloads are running.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: Off</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Download History Length</title>
        <p>The amount of time to keep past downloads in the app's history.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: One Week</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
